37:13.710 --> 37:17.430
I GOT A LITTLE BIT
TENACIOUS THERE.

37:17.540 --> 37:19.053
BUT WILDS, WHY?
I MEAN,

37:19.160 --> 37:20.502
IT TAKES STRATEGY
OUT OF THE GAME.

37:20.610 --> 37:22.089
WHAT ARE WE HERE FOR,
YOU KNOW?

37:22.200 --> 37:23.360
- AND IT WASN'T
ABOUT THE WILDS.

37:23.480 --> 37:25.471
MY BROTHER-IN-LAW
HAS SOME OTHER STUFF GOING ON.

37:25.580 --> 37:28.401
SO DON'T WORRY ABOUT IT.
IT WASN'T YOU.

37:28.520 --> 37:31.375
- YOU LIKE CUBANOS?

37:31.490 --> 37:32.411
- WHAT, CIGARS?

37:32.520 --> 37:34.033
- YEAH.
- YEAH.

37:34.140 --> 37:36.199
- DIDN'T MENTION THESE BEFORE,
'CAUSE I ONLY BROUGHT TWO.

37:36.320 --> 37:37.696
- SECRET STASH.
THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

37:37.800 --> 37:41.110
- GOT THOSE FROM A GUY
WHO OWNS AN ALLIGATOR.

37:41.220 --> 37:43.632
WAIT A MINUTE, DON'T--
LET ME CLIP IT.

37:43.740 --> 37:46.948
LISTEN...

37:47.050 --> 37:50.429
REMEMBER THE OTHER DAY I CAME BY
FOR DR. PELIKAN'S NUMBER?

37:50.540 --> 37:51.882
- YEAH, FOR THE OTHER THING.
[cigar cutter clicks]

37:51.990 --> 37:54.777
- YEAH, THE OTHER THING.

37:54.890 --> 37:57.165
THE OTHER THING IS ME.

37:57.270 --> 38:00.751
- WHAT? YOU?

38:00.860 --> 38:01.849
- YEAH. YEAH.

38:01.960 --> 38:03.780
I'VE BEEN THINKING
THAT MAYBE I MIGHT HAVE

38:03.900 --> 38:07.586
SOME OF THOSE
ASPERGER'S QUALITIES.

38:07.690 --> 38:08.930
YOU DIDN'T NOTICE ANYTHING?

38:09.040 --> 38:11.907
- NO, UH-UH. NOT AT ALL.

38:12.010 --> 38:16.595
I MEAN, MAYBE A LITTLE BIT
WITH THE WILD CARD THING.

38:16.700 --> 38:20.773
- I'M KIDDING. SO WHAT DID
DR. PELIKAN HAVE TO SAY?

38:20.880 --> 38:22.984
- JUMP BALL.

38:23.090 --> 38:26.298
COULD HAVE IT, COULD NOT.

38:26.400 --> 38:26.912
- HMM.

38:27.020 --> 38:30.604
- JUMP BALL.

38:30.720 --> 38:33.541
[Laura Marling's
When You Were Happy]

38:44.870 --> 38:47.759
- HEY, THERE,
NEW FRIEND ACROSS THE SEA

38:47.870 --> 38:51.761
IF YOU FIGURE THINGS OUT,
WOULD YOU FIGURE IN ME

38:56.090 --> 38:58.638
WOULDN'T IT BE A THING
TO LIVE SOMEWHERE

38:58.750 --> 38:59.774
QUIETLY WHERE THERE'S
A BREEZE

38:59.880 --> 39:03.156
AND THERE'S A REASON
FOR US TO BE

39:04.270 --> 39:06.545
- HEY.
DID YOU FORGET SOMETHING?

39:13.520 --> 39:17.035
- _YES.
- [glggleSJ

