- HEY THERE

39:19.010 --> 39:21.979
NEW FRIEND

39:22.080 --> 39:24.696
HMM, ACROSS THE SEA,
IF YOU FIGURE THINGS OUT

39:24.810 --> 39:25.799
WOULD YOU FIGURE IN ME

