I FIND

39:42.930 --> 39:45.581
THE MORE I

39:45.690 --> 39:48.989
THINK, THE HARDER IT IS
FOR ME TO BREATHE

39:55.010 --> 39:56.864
WHEN WERE

39:56.980 --> 39:59.175
WE HAPPY

39:59.290 --> 40:03.829
AND HOW LONG

40:03.950 --> 40:04.974
HAS THAT BEEN

40:10.580 --> 40:12.980
- I'M MOVING OUT, JULIA.

40:13.100 --> 40:16.024
- JOEL, PLEASE.

40:16.130 --> 40:19.019
- I'LL START LOOKING
FOR A PLACE TOMORROW.

40:34.600 --> 40:37.637
- [groans]
OHH...

40:52.450 --> 40:52.996
THANKS FOR LETTING ME
STAY HERE.

40:53.100 --> 40:55.091
- SURE.

40:55.210 --> 40:59.306
- THERE IS SOMEBODY
I'M LONGING TO SEE

40:59.420 --> 41:02.799
- LOOK, ABOUT LAST NIGHT...

41:02.900 --> 41:07.769
I JUST--I SAID SOME STUFF...

41:07.870 --> 41:11.215
- SOMEONE WHO'LL WATCH

41:11.330 --> 41:13.560
- I'M JUST SORRY.

41:13.670 --> 41:16.776
- OVER ME

41:16.880 --> 41:18.609
- REALLY...

41:18.710 --> 41:20.951
I REALLY GOTTA STOP
BEING SO MAD AT YOU.

41:21.060 --> 41:23.472
I GOTTA LET IT GO.

41:23.580 --> 41:26.469
- OH, HE MAY NOT
BE A GUY

41:26.580 --> 41:28.992
- WELL, YOU GOT A LOT
OFF YOUR CHEST,

41:29.100 --> 41:32.206
AND THEY SAY THAT HELPS.

41:32.310 --> 41:37.100
YOU KNOW, FOR THE RECORD, YOU--
[clears throat]

41:37.210 --> 41:39.519
YOU'RE NOT LIKE ME.

41:39.630 --> 41:42.007
IF YOU WERE,
YOU WOULDN'T STILL BE HERE.

41:42.120 --> 41:45.704
YOU'D OF LEI-T
WITHOUT SAYING GOOD-BYE.

41:45.810 --> 41:47.698
YOU COULD NEVER BE ME.

41:47.810 --> 41:48.913
- WON'T YOU TELL HIM,
PLEASE

41:49.020 --> 41:50.089
- 'CAUSE YOU GOT
YOUR MOTHER IN YOU.

41:50.190 --> 41:54.058
- TO PUT ON SOME SPEED

41:54.160 --> 41:57.573
FOLLOW MY LEAD

41:57.680 --> 41:59.500
'CAUSE, OH, HOW I NEED

41:59.620 --> 42:02.851
- MM. THESE ARE REALLY GOOD.

42:02.960 --> 42:03.949
- [chuckles]

42:04.070 --> 42:08.109
